Good afternoon, All,
Firstly, thank you Raffaella for allowing us to visit your property with yo=
u and to complete the additional reviews and assessment last Wednesday =E2=
=80=93 April 22. Your time is acknowledged and always appreciated.
I have spoken this morning with Stephen Walker, the Principal Consultant fo=
r ASURNZ, who will be authoring the response. Stephen has advised me that t=
his response should be sent to me to share with you all by the middle of ne=
xt week. Naturally =E2=80=93 I will forward this immediately if received be=
fore then.
Thank you again.
Regards,
Grant.

