<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good afternoon, All=
,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Firstly, thank you =
Raffaella for allowing us to visit your property with you and to complete t=
he additional reviews and assessment last Wednesday =E2=80=93 April 22. You=
r time is acknowledged and always appreciated.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I have spoken this =
morning with Stephen Walker, the Principal Consultant for ASURNZ, who will =
be authoring the response. Stephen has advised me that this response should=
 be sent to me to share with you all
 by the middle of next week. Naturally =E2=80=93 I will forward this immedi=
ately if received before then.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Thank you again.<o:=
p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regards,<o:p></o:p>=
</span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant. <o:p></o:p><=
/span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
