he house is certainly available, but that time isn=E2=80=99t ideal =E2=80=
=93 my client is overseas at the moment, due back in to NZ (but not
 Auckland) on Wednesday night. There are strikes affecting travel too. Woul=
d you be free late afternoon one day next week instead?<o:p></o:p></span></=
